        "custom_liquid_JrCkxb": {
          "type": "custom_liquid",
          "settings": {
            "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"accordion\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"accordion-toggle\"><label class=\"accordion-label\" for=\"accordion-toggle\">Product Description</label><div class=\"accordion-content\"><h6>NG EarSafe Pro Mini Open-Ear Bone Conduction Headphones – Wireless, Lightweight & Built for All-Day Comfort</h6><p><span class=\"highlight\">🔊 Hear the World, Feel the Beat</span><br>Introducing the NG EarSafe Pro Mini, the ultimate fusion of safety, comfort, and next-generation technology. Developed with bone conduction technology, these wireless headphones keep your ears open to your surroundings while delivering crisp, immersive sound. Perfect for workouts, calls, and all-day wear!</p><p><span class=\"highlight\">Why You’ll Love It:</span></p><ul><li><strong>Open-Ear Bone Conduction Tech:</strong> Enjoy your music without blocking out the world. Stay aware, stay safe!</li><li><strong>Dual ENC Mic with Crystal-Clear Calls:</strong> Noise-canceling mics ensure your voice is heard, even in noisy environments.</li><li><strong>Next-Gen BT 5.3 Connectivity:</strong> Faster, stronger, and ultra-stable pairing for seamless audio.</li><li><strong>Built to Endure – IPX6 Splash & Dustproof:</strong> Sweat, rain, or dust? No worries—just keep moving!</li><li><strong>Super Fast Charging, Always Ready:</strong> 10 minutes = 70% charge, so you’re never left waiting.</li><li><strong>Long-Lasting Power:</strong> Up to 9 hours of continuous playtime and 72-hour standby to fuel your adventures.</li><li><strong>Effortless Control:</strong> One-button operation for track changes and call management.</li><li><strong>Premium Comfort:</strong> Full silicone finish with a lightweight (24g) titanium wraparound design for a snug, secure fit.</li></ul><p><span class=\"highlight\">🎧 Your Sound, Your Style</span><br>Upgrade to the NG EarSafe Pro Mini and experience the freedom of wireless, open-ear listening like never before! 🚀</p></div></div>\n\n<style>\n.accordion{width:450px;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:5px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:15px;}.accordion input{display:none}.accordion-label{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:5px 20px;color:#252525;cursor:pointer;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;transition:background-color .3s ease}.accordion-label::after{content:'▼';font-size:16px;transition:transform 0.3s ease}.accordion input:checked+.accordion-label::after{transform:rotate(180deg)}.accordion-content{max-height:0;overflow:auto;padding:0 20px;background-color:#fff;color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;transition:max-height 0.4s ease,padding 0.3s ease}.accordion input:checked~.accordion-content{max-height:500px;padding:15px 20px}.accordion-content h6{margin-top:0;color:#28486e}.accordion-content ul{margin:10px 0;padding-left:20px}.accordion-content ul li{list-style-type:disc;margin-bottom:8px}.accordion-content p{margin:10px 0}.accordion-content .highlight{font-weight:bold}\n@media only screen and (max-width: 768px) {.accordion{width:100%}}\n</style>"
          }
